2007-10-09  Jim Meyering  <meyering@redhat.com>

	Move the help-version test into misc/.
	* tests/help-version: Move to...
	* tests/misc/help-version: ...here.
	Source test-lib.sh, as usual.
	Use $abs_top_builddir, rather than ".." and "../..".

