	xreadlink-with-size. Add xreadlink.
	* src/copy.c (copy_internal): Update.
	* src/ls.c (is_directory): Update.
	* src/stat.c (print_stat): Update.
	* src/readlink.c (main): Use the one-argument xreadlink function.

